    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-03-28T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-03-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="562"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d562">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Porter</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-03-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 28, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Corner stone of monument to Rochambeau has been laid at Vendôme, home of family.
                    French and American flags have been raised on the grounds. Organization
                    committee desire me to send their friendly greetings to the President and people
                    of America.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Porter.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
